<TEXT>
The European Court yesterday rejected a complaint by the French holding
company Matra-Hachette against plans by Ford of the US and Volkswagen of
Germany to build a minivan assembly plant in Portugal.
Matra-Hachette, which builds Espace minivans for French car maker Renault,
