<TEXT>
Minolta Camera of Japan has announced the formation of two joint ventures in
China in October to manufacture and market cameras and copier machines,
Reuter reports from Tokyo.
One joint venture will be formed in Shanghai with China's largest camera
maker, Shanghai Camera Factory.
