    HKZ  Hong Kong, Asia.
    MYZ  Malaysia, Asia.
    SGZ  Singapore, Asia.
    THZ  Thailand, Asia.
    CNZ  China, Asia.
    IDZ  Indonesia, Asia.
</CN>
