<HEADLINE>
FT  15 JUL 94 / Memorial service for John Smith
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Politicians from all parties gathered at Westminster Abbey yesterday to pay
tribute to former Labour leader John Smith. Leadership hopeful John Prescott
was among Labour MPs attending, with his wife Pauline
</TEXT>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
