Wednesday are desperate attempts to try to prevent the public using the
services available.' He emphasised that 'not one train will run on a strike
day or any other day unless Railtrack is absolutely satisfied that the
service meets the requirements of safety'.
The RMT has already decided to call a further one-day strike for next
Wednesday.
